---
title: Smoky Tex-Mex Beef Meatballs with Scallion-Garlic Rice and Feta
description: In this enticing dinner, beef meatballs get tossed in a smoky chipotle sauce that's lightly sweetened with bell peppers and tomatoes. The delicious mixture is heaped on a fragrant mound of scallion-garlic rice with a sprinkle of feta acting as the perfect topper!
